## Key Improvements Made

### Architecture (7 fixes)
1. **Data source pattern** for Quick Pitch modal - Single source of truth prevents content drift
2. **PPR with conditional rendering** (Next.js 15/16) - Eliminates flash of wrong content, latest paradigm
3. **RSS build integration** using `rss` npm package - Auto-generates on deploy
4. **Zod schema validation** for blog frontmatter - Fails build on invalid metadata
5. **WebGL context loss handler** - Degrades gracefully to CSS-only UI
6. **Vercel Image Optimization** specified - Automatic optimization, zero config
7. **Git as backup** - Document recovery commands, no additional infra needed

### Code Quality (5 fixes)
1. **Shader component library** pattern - Prevents code duplication, single source of truth
2. **Performance monitoring cooldown** - Particles re-enable after 5s, recover from transient slowdowns
3. **TypeScript strict mode** - Catch bugs at compile time, essential for WebGL debugging
4. **ESLint + Prettier** - Consistent style, bug prevention
5. **Error boundary strategy** - Graceful error handling with retry button

### Testing (10 additions)
1. **Full test coverage strategy** approved (extends timeline 1-2 weeks)
2. **Unit tests** (Jest + React Testing Library) - Components, utilities, shaders
3. **E2E tests** (Playwright) - VC journey, engineer journey, mobile, accessibility
4. **Integration tests** - Blog pipeline, RSS generation
5. **Performance tests** - Lighthouse CI, bundle size monitoring
6. **Test plan artifact** created at `~/.gstack/projects/portfolio/aryaniyaps-master-eng-review-test-plan-20260413-085407.md`

### Performance (5 fixes)
1. **Dynamic import WebGL** - Saves 500KB on mobile, never loads unused code
2. **Lazy load blog images** - Eager load first, lazy load rest
3. **RSS cache invalidation** - Skip generation if no blog changes
4. **Memory budget** - 100MB limit + cleanup prevents leaks
5. **Performance monitoring** - Frame time checks with cooldown logic

